        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5">
            <strong>
          Summary: Russia and Ukraine exchanged attacks hours after Trump’s ultimatum. </strong>
          </p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5">
        <strong>The what:</strong> At least 22 people were killed in a <a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #06266D; color: black;" href="https://link.geopoliticalsummary.com/gs-30-jul-25-spotlight-h2-5-russian-missile-and-drone-attack?source=website" target="_blank">Russian missile and drone attack</a> over 73 cities, towns, and villages. Four Russian glide bombs hit a prison in Ukraine's southeastern Zaporizhzhia region, killing at least 17 and injuring 80. Their missiles destroyed emergency care facilities in the Dnipro region of central Ukraine. These strikes occurred hours after Trump threatened Putin with sanctions if Russia continued its attacks. 
          </p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5">
         <strong>The warning:</strong> The Kremlin spokesman said that Russia is determined to achieve its goals in Ukraine and confirmed that they have noted Trump’s warnings. However, the former president of Russia warned that every ultimatum issued is a threat and a step towards war, not just with Ukraine but also with the US. Russia had earlier warned that the involvement of Western powers could push the war to NATO countries. 
          </p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5">
         <strong>The reaction:</strong> The Ukrainian military launched a drone attack on Russia, targeting oil depots, weapons plants, and disrupting commercial flights. The Russian Defense Ministry confirmed that it intercepted 74 drones. Meanwhile, hacker groups claiming to be Ukrainian supporters led a <a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #06266D; color: black;" href="https://link.geopoliticalsummary.com/gs-30-jul-25-spotlight-h2-6-major-cyberattack?source=website" target="_blank">major cyberattack</a> on the Stolichki pharmacy chain, resulting in a temporary closure. 
          </p>
